{"tid":2037572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣人角度看香港抗爭","createTime":"2020-05-27T05:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T06:46:17.000Z","uid":241151,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"386c11bdf4f01d23c4f9ef2551157aebb78511eb","tid":2037572,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:23:15.000Z","msg":"去年反送中期間有兩件事讓我印象深刻，一件是台灣有媒體報導，香港人來台灣五金街買口罩，寫得有點太過詳細。那之後的一週內，香港人從台灣回去就開始被查行李。另一件是理工大學圍城，有人從路橋逃脫的影片流出之後，那條路線馬上就被港警堵住。<br />\n<br />\n不管你有什麼正當的理由，救援行動就是必須低調 。林榮基一定也很清楚。這也就是為什麼我徹底看不起雞屎黃白，你們是用別人的生命風險在炒你們的政治資本，我真的很想直接扔這些混蛋下地獄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabc8c760073eaacf510fc8def9f4bbc0638dda1","tid":2037572,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:28:47.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"36bc3c34a6250877f647a95de0d87dc72ba9aa2a","tid":2037572,"uid":107951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZDLnnka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDLnnka.jpg&h=e7249233&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8aa98a52deb156254a0666f6c332cef64c1f3c9","tid":2037572,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"36bc3c34a6250877f647a95de0d87dc72ba9aa2a","tid":2037572,"uid":107951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZDLnnka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDLnnka.jpg&h=e7249233&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T06:00:24.000Z","msg":"你死開啦左膠"},{"pid":"2a6083d40ed7f1c6007dea6c98af321271195a16","tid":2037572,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"熱狗黎"},{"pid":"0c4b8541f6a9034fa7a7c49de815f44e010c8109","tid":2037572,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2a6083d40ed7f1c6007dea6c98af32127